"#feedbackModal_main_3614741\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 11, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104nbl1665703095768.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/nbl1665703095768.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/nbl1665703095768.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"nbl1665703095768\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      ScrollButtons\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Images to use for the left and right scroll buttons.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"nbl1665703095768__p_d106847e1_d106848e1_d106849e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">\"</code>ScrollButtons<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">ImageList</var><code class=\"ph codeph\">\"</code></p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"nbl1665703095768__table_d12602e1_d12603e1_d12604e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"nbl1665703095768__table_d12602e1_d12603e1_d12604e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Value</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"nbl1665703095768__table_d12602e1_d12603e1_d12604e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Description</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nbl1665703095768__table_d12602e1_d12603e1_d12604e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">List</var>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nbl1665703095768__table_d12602e1_d12603e1_d12604e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Comma-separated list of two image or glyph names; for example:</p>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">@<var class=\"keyword varname\">LeftImageFile</var>, @<var class=\"keyword varname\">RightImageFile</var>\n</code>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">^<var class=\"keyword varname\">LeftGlyphName</var>, \n                                    <code class=\"ph codeph\">^<var class=\"keyword varname\">RightGlyphName</var>\n</code>\n</code>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\">If only one image is specified, the property is ignored.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"nbl1665703095768__section_rdt_f2k_zwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1148295e143\">Usage</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"nbl1665703095768__table_d12605e1_d12606e1_d12607e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">Dynamic?</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">Yes</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">Supported in Grid?</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">No</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">Dependencies:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">Only works for a single-line, horizontal tab strip</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"nbl1665703095768__section_lwr_h2k_zwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1148295e206\">Description</h2>This property only works for a\n         single-line, horizontal tab strip, and if a <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Default Image</span> is\n            defined.<p class=\"p\" id=\"nbl1665703095768__p_d106865e1_d106866e1_d106867e1\">If two images are defined, they are\n            positioned to the left and the right of the tab strip. The size is determined by the\n            height of the tab strip. The width of the buttons are determined by the image\n            width.</p><p class=\"p\" id=\"nbl1665703095768__p_d106868e1_d106869e1_d106870e1\">If no  ScrollButtons are defined, default scroll buttons are\n            displayed in the default Windows representation and location (both buttons appear in the\n            right-hand corner of the scroll bar).</p></section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"nbl1665703095768__section_izf_42k_zwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1148295e221\">Using in ProcScript</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"nbl1665703095768__p_d106874e1_d106875e1_d106876e1\">You can use <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$properties</span> or\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$fieldproperties</span> to set or get the property and its value. For\n            more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"zie1665702558978.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zie1665702558978.html\" title=\"Return or set the current widget properties of a field.\">$properties</a> and <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"aud1705998763272.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/aud1705998763272.html\" title=\"Return or set the current widget properties of an instance of a field.\">$fieldproperties</a>.</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"nbl1665703095768__pre_akw_q2k_zwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">$fieldproperties(FLD) = \"scrollbuttons=@left.png,@right.png\"</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"nbl1665703095768__section_cnb_r2k_zwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1148295e254\">Applies To</h2>\n<p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gyf1688451219719.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gyf1688451219719.html\" title=\"The utabex widget enables users to navigate through a collection of contained forms by clicking a tab to display the form. The utabex widget is highly customizable, allowing extensive control over the appearance and behavior of the tabs. Uniface provides a logical widget called TabEx, which is mapped to utabex.\">utabex (TabEx)</a></p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dte1665702632952.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Default Image (ImgDefault)</a><p>The image that is displayed as the button or tab.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3614741\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3614741\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "ScrollButtons Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 11, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 ScrollButtons Images to use for the left and right scroll buttons. \" ScrollButtons = ImageList \" Value Description List Comma-separated list of two image or glyph names; for example: @ LeftImageFile , @ RightImageFile ^ LeftGlyphName , ^ RightGlyphName If only one image is specified, the property is ignored. Usage Dynamic? Yes Supported in Grid? No Dependencies: Only works for a single-line, horizontal tab strip Description This property only works for a single-line, horizontal tab strip, and if a Default Image is defined. If two images are defined, they are positioned to the left and the right of the tab strip. The size is determined by the height of the tab strip. The width of the buttons are determined by the image width. If no ScrollButtons are defined, default scroll buttons are displayed in the default Windows representation and location (both buttons appear in the right-hand corner of the scroll bar). Using in ProcScript You can use $properties or $fieldproperties to set or get the property and its value. For more information, see $properties and $fieldproperties . $fieldproperties(FLD) = \"scrollbuttons=@left.png,@right.png\" Copy Applies To utabex (TabEx) Related Links Default Image (ImgDefault) The image that is displayed as the button or tab. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}